    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1929-11-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1929-11-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="698"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d698">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">817.00/6459</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hanna</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-11-05">November 5,
                            1929</date>.<lb/>[Received November 11.]</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 1220</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: With reference to my despatch No. 1203 of October
                    26, 1929, I have the honor to report that Señor Paguaga Núñez, the Director of
                        <hi rend="italic">La Prensa</hi>, was released from the local penitentiary
                    on October 30 after paying a fine of C$40.00 imposed by the Local Police Judge.
                    The reason for the fine as explained by <hi rend="italic">La Prensa</hi> the
                    following day was the publication of the editorial transmitted with my despatch
                    No. 1203, entitled “Those of the Surrender and Youth”.<note n="44"
                        xml:id="d698fn44">Editorial not reprinted.</note>
                </p>
                <p>I have [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Matthew E. Hanna</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
